{"word":"ὑπερβασία","slug":"ὑπερβασία","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ὑπερβασία</b></el> <el>(ὑπερβᾰσία, ἡ,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ὑπερβαίνω'><el>ὑπερβαίνω</el></a>\n<p/><i>a transgression of law, trespass</i>, <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>: also in <a href='S:plural'>pl.</a>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b><p/>"}]}